'''Benjamin Ze'ev (Theodor) Herzl''' ([[tahungarit]]: '''Herzl Tivadar''', [[taɛebrit]]: '''בנימין זאב הרצל''' (''Binyomin Ze'ev Hertzl'')) (2 Mayyu, 1860 – 3 Yulyu, 1904) yella d aneɣmas uday n tmurt Uṭric-Maǧer, d netta i d-isnulfan zionizm.

Herzl ilul di Budapest, Maǧer, yezdeɣ di Vienne di temẓi-s u yeɣra dinna azref, lameɛna yuɣal-d aneɣmas. 
Di turuft n lqern 19, tella aṭas [[tamgelsamit]] (antisémitisme), ilmend lḥal-agi Herzl yebɣa ad ijemmeɛ akk udayen di yiwen tmurt, [[israyil]], tasnakta-yagi tettusemma zionism..

